  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705640/extras/f100b6bd11f61b6ad163179ca7e77936.avif?t=1523273683\" width=600 height=147 /></span><br>BACK TO THE EGG! is a modern tower defense game with action-rpg elements.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dynamic fight system.<br></li><li> Intuitive build system.<br></li><li> Upgradable towers.<br></li><li> Several maps and waves with different difficulties.<br></li><li> Compete with other players for supremacy on leaderboards!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705640/extras/3d37528068651f0d63fd27d05955bde6.avif?t=1523273683\" width=600 height=147 /></span><br><br>BACK TO THE EGG! is still in an early stage and will become a lot better and BIGGER over the next months. Our aim is to ship significant updates every 2-4 weeks.<br><br>If you want to know more about our plans and what the current players are thinking then check out our discord channel: ",
